How many orders were shipped by Speedy Express in total?

SELECT count(ord.shipperid) as Total_Orders, ship.Shipper_ID, ship.Shipper_Name
from orders as ord, shippers as ship,
WHERE  ord.shipperid= shippers.shipperid
GROUP BY Total_Orders

The total number of orders shipped by Speedy Express was 54. 

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

What is the last name of the employee with the most orders?

SELECT count(ord.orderid) as Total_Orders, ord.employeeid as Employee_ID, emp.lastname as Last_Name
from orders as ord, employees as emp
WHERE  ord.employeeid=emp.employeeid
GROUP BY Employee_ID

The last name of the employee with the most orders is Peacock. 

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

What product was ordered the most by customers in Germany?
select sum(od.Quantity) as Total_Orders, pro.productname as Product_Name, sup.Country 
from orderdetails as od, suppliers as sup, products as pro
where od.productid = pro.productid and sup.supplierid = pro.supplierid and country = 'Germany' 
GROUP BY ProductName

The product that was the most ordered in Germany was Gumbär Gummibärchen

